Governor Seyi Makinde, on Wednesday, approved the ap­pointment of Professor Ola­wale Olakulehin as Acting Chief Medical Director of LAUTECH Teaching Hospi­tal, Ogbomoso. This was contained in a statement signed by the Chief of Staff to the Governor, Otunba Segun Ogunwuyi. According to the state­ment, the appointment was with immediate effect. The governor, while con­gratulating the new appoin­tee, asked him to see his ap­pointment as a call to service and urged him to discharge his duty with absolute loyalty, dedication and diligence.